      <div class="eight columns">
        <h3>Sponsor us.</h3>
<p class="section">
  The Italian Ruby Day, is the official annual gathering of Ruby developers in Italy.
  Founded in 2011, RubyDay 2012 is the 2nd installment of this event. RubyDay has 
  been the italian venue for announcements regarding the Ruby programming language 
  usage to show people works, compare notes and involve the community.
</p>

<h3>Why should you sponsor RubyDay?</h3>
<p class="section">
<strong>Visible event</strong>. Many of the most prominent and influential community members 
present widely publicized and discussed internet-wide. Seats sell out quickly, so sponsorship 
guarantees a spot. Last, the community provides an opportunity to connect with many Ruby 
developers one on one. The following sponsorship opportunities are available.

<h3>Golden sponsor | ‚Ç¨ 1.000</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Sponsor designation in our marketing efforts</li>
  <li>Large ad in RubyConf program</li>
  <li>Large banner style logo on conference website</li>
  <li>Sponsor may distribute pamphlets at the conference</li>
  <li>Announcement before the plenary session</li>
</ol>

<h3>Silver sponsor | ‚Ç¨ 500</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Sponsor designation in our marketing efforts</li>
  <li>Medium ad in RubyConf program</li>
  <li>Medium banner style logo on conference website</li>
  <li>Sponsor may distribute pamphlets at the conference</li>
  <li>Announcement before the plenary session</li>
</ol>

<h3>Media sponsor | Communication</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Sponsor designation in our marketing efforts</li>
  <li>Small ad in RubyConf program</li>
  <li>Small banner style logo on conference website</li>
  <li>Announcement before the plenary session</li>
</ol>

<p>
  If you have an idea for a custom sponsorship please contact us. We‚Äôd love to discuss your ideas.
</p>
     </div>


