          <span class="fl">I</span>f you (or would love to) use Ruby, BDD, NodeJS, MongoDB, Amazon WS
          and you love building and thinking about clean and consistent architectures that connect 
          to the physical world <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>
      </li>

      <li id="integrator" class="box resume">
        <a href="/about/#touch"><span class="strap">Device Integrator</span> 
        <span class="label"><span>C</span>onnect <span>A</span>ll <span>S</span>tandards</span></a>
