        <span class="fl">Y</span>our life is to spend days and days between social networks, to find new ideas
        that makes you cooler and to catch the attention of all the crowd. If you also believe in what we do
        <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>
      </li>

      <li id="interaction" class="box resume">
        <a href="/about/#touch"><span class="strap">Interaction Hacker</span>
        <span class="label"><span>V</span>oice, <span>T</span>ouch <span></span>and <span>M</span>ore</span></a>
