          <span class="fl">W</span>e get lot of data which could be used to improve the way we live in our 
          houses. If you love finding patterns, visualizing data, and you feel confortable moving 
          around lot of data, 
          <a href="/about/#touch" class="dest">get in touch with us ‚Üí</a>        
      </li>

      <li id="security" class="box resume">
